Package Datastructures.Literals

Klasse CLiteral

java.lang.Object
Datastructures.Literals.CLiteral
Alle implementierten Schnittstellen:
Positioned
public class CLiteral extends Object implements Positioned
Created by Ohlbach on 25.08.2018.
A CLiteral is a literal within a clause.
Besides the literal, it contains a pointer to the clause and the clausePosition within the clause. A CLiteral can be subclassed to carry more information.
